47.title: McDermott vs Lang
47.plot: Family Feud is an Australian family television game show for all ages. Family Feud is a quiz show, where the host asks one question and the team captains buzz in and give their answer without their team's help. Out of both the team captains, whoever gets the highest score chooses to Pass or Play. If they Play, they can take a shot at answering all the questions; if they Pass, the other team attempts to answer all the questions. There are three rounds and and only one team can win the game at the end of the programme.
